        "enunciado_html":  "\u003cdiv style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"margin-bottom: 0;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #00f0ff;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eT\u0026iacute;tulo de Especialista em Medicina Intensiva\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003ePara classifica\u0026ccedil;\u0026atilde;o de perfus\u0026atilde;o em estado de choque podemos utilizar o mottling score (imagem a seguir), cuja gradua\u0026ccedil;\u0026atilde;o vai de score 1 a score 5.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://medreviewflashcards.s3.sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/questoes_images/T90IA0jkpVmVa6exzvzDca9aNzy2WYnHbqavuDSQ.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"60%\" /\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eSobre essa vari\u0026aacute;vel, assinale a alternativa correta.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e",
