        "gabarito":  "B",
        "comentario_html":  "\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #f3c99f;\"\u003eGABARITO LETRA B: II.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #ffffff;\"\u003eA curva de press\u0026atilde;o venosa central \u0026eacute; composta por oscila\u0026ccedil;\u0026otilde;es mec\u0026acirc;nicas divididas em tr\u0026ecirc;s deflex\u0026otilde;es positivas, chamadas de ondas, e duas deflex\u0026otilde;es negativas, denominadas descensos. Esses componentes refletem diretamente os eventos mec\u0026acirc;nicos e el\u0026eacute;tricos do ciclo card\u0026iacute;aco direito.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #ffffff;\"\u003e➡️ \u003cspan style=\"color: #f8a323;\"\u003eOnda a:\u003c/span\u003e representa a s\u0026iacute;stole ou contra\u0026ccedil;\u0026atilde;o ativa do \u0026aacute;trio direito, ocorrendo logo ap\u0026oacute;s a onda P do eletrocardiograma, no final da di\u0026aacute;stole ventricular.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #ffffff;\"\u003e➡️ \u003cspan style=\"color: #f8a323;\"\u003eOnda c:\u003c/span\u003e surge no in\u0026iacute;cio da s\u0026iacute;stole ventricular e decorre do fechamento e do abaulamento da valva tric\u0026uacute;spide em dire\u0026ccedil;\u0026atilde;o ao \u0026aacute;trio durante a contra\u0026ccedil;\u0026atilde;o isovolum\u0026eacute;trica.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #ffffff;\"\u003e➡️ \u003cspan style=\"color: #f8a323;\"\u003eDescenso x:\u003c/span\u003e reflete o relaxamento atrial simult\u0026acirc;neo ao esvaziamento do ventr\u0026iacute;culo, associado \u0026agrave; tra\u0026ccedil;\u0026atilde;o caudal da base do cora\u0026ccedil;\u0026atilde;o e da valva atrioventricular durante a s\u0026iacute;stole.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #ffffff;\"\u003e➡️ \u003cspan style=\"color: #f8a323;\"\u003eOnda v:\u003c/span\u003e corresponde ao enchimento atrial passivo pelo retorno venoso sist\u0026ecirc;mico, que ocorre no final da s\u0026iacute;stole ventricular enquanto a valva tric\u0026uacute;spide permanece fechada.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #ffffff;\"\u003e➡️ \u003cspan style=\"color: #f8a323;\"\u003eDescenso y:\u003c/span\u003e representa o esvaziamento r\u0026aacute;pido do \u0026aacute;trio e o enchimento ventricular precoce imediatamente ap\u0026oacute;s a abertura da valva tric\u0026uacute;spide, marcando o in\u0026iacute;cio da di\u0026aacute;stole ventricular.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #00ffff;\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://medreviewflashcards.s3.sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/questoes_images/MTn9ejdqZOhN8etnz8GaX2hXUUZ8xMyEGVu8XDqX.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"50%\" data-id=\"questoes_images/MTn9ejdqZOhN8etnz8GaX2hXUUZ8xMyEGVu8XDqX.png\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #ffffff;\"\u003eQuando a quest\u0026atilde;o fala sobre definir pr\u0026eacute;-carga atrav\u0026eacute;s da press\u0026atilde;o venosa central, o que ela quer dizer: \u0026eacute; em que ponto da curva de PVC melhor se reflete a press\u0026atilde;o diast\u0026oacute;lica final do ventr\u0026iacute;culo direito?\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #ffffff;\"\u003eOra, se a contra\u0026ccedil;\u0026atilde;o ventricular come\u0026ccedil;a no in\u0026iacute;cio do QRS, queremos o ponto da curva que coincide com esse in\u0026iacute;cio, representando a transi\u0026ccedil;\u0026atilde;o entre o final da di\u0026aacute;stole e o in\u0026iacute;cio da s\u0026iacute;stole. Esse ponto corresponde ao ponto 2 do desenho, que \u0026eacute; a transi\u0026ccedil;\u0026atilde;o entre a \u003cspan style=\"color: #f8a323;\"\u003eonda a\u003c/span\u003e, contra\u0026ccedil;\u0026atilde;o atrial, e a \u003cspan style=\"color: #f8a323;\"\u003eonda c\u003c/span\u003e, fechamento da v\u0026aacute;lvula tric\u0026uacute;spide.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #f3c99f;\"\u003eVAMOS ANALISAR CADA UMA DAS ALTERNATIVAS\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #f57477;\"\u003eA) I. (INCORRETO)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eO algarismo I indica o pico da \u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #f8a323;\"\u003eonda a\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e, que representa a contra\u0026ccedil;\u0026atilde;o atrial ativa. Embora fa\u0026ccedil;a parte da di\u0026aacute;stole ventricular, esse pico press\u0026oacute;rico ocorre antes do completo enchimento ventricular. Por isso, ele n\u0026atilde;o reflete com precis\u0026atilde;o a press\u0026atilde;o diast\u0026oacute;lica final, que define a pr\u0026eacute;-carga.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #94bd7b;\"\u003eB) II. (CORRETO)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eA indica\u0026ccedil;\u0026atilde;o II representa o \u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #f8a323;\"\u003eponto Z\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e, situado na jun\u0026ccedil;\u0026atilde;o e base da subida da \u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #f8a323;\"\u003eonda c\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e. Esse local reflete o exato final da di\u0026aacute;stole ventricular, ocorrendo logo ap\u0026oacute;s a s\u0026iacute;stole atrial. Ele \u0026eacute; a estimativa mais fidedigna da pr\u0026eacute;-carga por anteceder o fechamento valvar.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #f57477;\"\u003eC) III. (INCORRETO)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eEm III, observa-se o pico da \u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #f8a323;\"\u003eonda c\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e, gerado pelo abaulamento valvar durante a s\u0026iacute;stole ventricular inicial. Esse \u0026eacute; um fen\u0026ocirc;meno puramente sist\u0026oacute;lico decorrente da fase de contra\u0026ccedil;\u0026atilde;o isovolum\u0026eacute;trica. Consequentemente, sua mensura\u0026ccedil;\u0026atilde;o superestima o volume diast\u0026oacute;lico final e distorce a avalia\u0026ccedil;\u0026atilde;o da pr\u0026eacute;-carga.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #f57477;\"\u003eD) IV. (INCORRETO)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eA onda identificada em IV corresponde \u0026agrave; \u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #f8a323;\"\u003eonda v\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e, decorrente do enchimento atrial passivo enquanto a valva atrioventricular permanece fechada. Trata-se de um evento sist\u0026oacute;lico tardio que culmina pr\u0026oacute;ximo \u0026agrave; onda T do eletrocardiograma. Portanto, esse ponto \u0026eacute; totalmente inadequado para avaliar a pr\u0026eacute;-carga.\u003c/p\u003e"
