        "enunciado_html":  "\u003cdiv style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"margin-bottom: 0;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #00f0ff;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eT\u0026iacute;tulo de Especialista em Medicina Intensiva\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eA press\u0026atilde;o de pulso arterial \u0026eacute; uma vari\u0026aacute;vel importante na avalia\u0026ccedil;\u0026atilde;o hemodin\u0026acirc;mica. Nos pacientes graves, \u0026eacute; adequado considerar que a press\u0026atilde;o de pulso arterial:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e",
